{"tid":1463143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理飛］大家會唔會考慮下block國泰以外櫃位","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:42:03.000Z","uid":269125,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"47da8177391a655f256fd7c1ec0fa9828149c208","tid":1463143,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:13:15.000Z","msg":"我唔係好認同block死，我覺得最少留一條路俾人走<br />\n咁黑狗都無藉口清場<br />\n但無論點都要block的話，應該要block幾間內地航空公司既check in櫃位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">812政府要block機場係因為所有航班都唔夠人起飛</span></span><br />\n大家嚟唔切check in<br />\n最後所有航班都要delay，航空時間表turn唔返<br />\n所以全部都要停<br />\n<br />\n由此可見，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">阻counter都會有一樣既效果</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可能會有人屌我，咁點解要放生國泰呀，佢地唔俾員工參加集會喎<br />\n但大家要諗中共依家集中火力搞國泰<br />\n太古同土共不嬲唔friend<br />\n亞太地區既航空一哥依舊係國泰<br />\n所以土共先借機搞國泰<br />\n<br />\n於是學毛主席話<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">凡是敵人反對的 我們就要擁護</span></span><br />\n我地應該放生國泰<br />\n<br />\n（睇下要食幾多負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfe7eec78cff3abe50a01d2209038c3008b7adf","tid":1463143,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:13:57.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong Express  都係國泰"},{"pid":"edc39c7e7401bebd34d57080581f185ee26e582b","tid":1463143,"uid":269125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:14:01.000Z","msg":"要jam not block<br />\n無論如何都要block<br />\n請策略性block"},{"pid":"78da2a754169c5c8bb8bee16d95f2d5f51ce61e2","tid":1463143,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:14:19.000Z","msg":"凡是敵人反對的 我們就要擁護"},{"pid":"7d7ae5ec9297654661067b8f66429a06391b0d05","tid":1463143,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:14:34.000Z","msg":"都話塞路3條塞2條留一條比人走已經做到效果<br />\n塞死只會越黎越衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"